<dd>British Medical Journal
<p>
<dt><a href="aer.html">Aerosolized surfactant in adults with sepsis-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome</a>
<dd>New England Journal Of Medicine
<p>

<dt><a href="hep.html">Viral dynamics in hepatitis B virus infection</a>
<dd>Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the USA<p>
<dt><a href="chelates.html">Iron chelates bind nitric oxide and decrease mortality in an experimental model of septic shock</a>
<dd>Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the USA<p>
<dt><a href="cloning.html">Cloning, expression, and distribution of a Ca2+-activated K+ channel beta-subunit from human brain</a>
<dd>Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the USA<p>
<dt><a href="bcell.html">B-Cell-Specific coactivator OBF-1 OCA-B/BOB1 required for immune response and germinal centre formation</a>
<dd>Nature<p>
