<h2><font size=6>14. Segment information</font></h2>
<p>

 <font size=5>The Group continues to operate in a single business segment.  	An analysis of turnover, profit before taxation and net assets by geographical segment is set out below. </font><p>


 The Group's activities are organised on a worldwide basis.  The segmental figures are therefore influenced by the location of the Group's operating resources and by variations over time in intra group trading and funding arrangements.  Comparative figures for 1994 have been restated for the change in accounting policy described in <a href="2.html">Note 2</a> and to reflect the current presentation of net assets.<p>


