<html><head>
<title>Preliminary results</title></head><body 
background="back1.gif" bgcolor="#ffffff" 
text="#000000" link="#1a1afa" vlink="30aa30">
<basefont size=4>

<a href="index.html"><img src="icon.gif" align=left border=0></a>
<br clear=left>

<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>Preliminary results</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>

<h2><font size=6>1. General</font></h2>
<p>
<font size=5>The Profit and Loss Account and Cash Flow Statement for the 18 months ended, and the Balance Sheet at, 31st December 1995 are subject to completion of the audit.</font><p>

 The Profit and Loss Account and Cash Flow Statement for the year ended, and the Balance Sheet, at 30th June 1994 are an abridged statement of the full Group accounts for that year, restated for the change of accounting policy described in Note 2 below, which have been delivered to the Registrar of Companies.  The report of the auditors on the Accounts for that year was unqualified and did not contain a statement under either section 237(2) or section 237(3) of the Companies Act 1985.<p>

<a href="2.html">Forward to: Accounting policies</a><p>
<a href="index.html">Return to: Notes contents page</a><p>




  

