<a href="http://www.glaxowellcome.co.uk/intexpl/bookmark/">Bookmarks</a> |
<a href="http://www.glaxowellcome.co.uk/intexpl/index.html">GW Homepage</a>
</font>
</ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>
