<ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>Preliminary results</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>

<h2><font size=6>Notes on the preliminary results</font></h2>

<ol>
  <li><a href="1.html">General</a>
  <li><a href="2.html">Accounting policies</a>
  <li><a href="3.html">Exchange rates</a>
  <li><a href="4.html">Operating costs</a>
  <li><a href="5.html">Profit on disposal of business</a>
