<DOCNO>WT14-B39-154</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA057-000937-B017-197</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/netscape/world/geneva/il5.html 193.128.22.20 19970109093217 text/html 4269
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 09:22:29 GMT
