http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/intexpl/science/actiontb/news2/art1.html 193.128.22.20 19970109095145 text/html 4560
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 09:41:57 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 24-Dec-96 11:29:54 GMT
