<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/intexpl/science/actiontb/news2/art5.html 193.128.22.20 19970109095245 text/html 3861
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 09:42:49 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 24-Dec-96 11:29:55 GMT
