<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>
<h2><font size=6>Set SlabMode</font></h2><p>
<pre>
Syntax:  set slabmode &lt;slabmode&gt;
</pre><p>
The RasMol
<tt><b>slabmode</b></tt>
parameter controls the rendering method of objects cut by the
slabbing (z-clipping) plane. Valid slabmode parameters are
"<tt><b>reject</b></tt>", "<tt><b>half</b></tt>",
"<tt><b>hollow</b></tt>", "<tt><b>solid</b></tt>" and
"<tt><b>section</b></tt>".

<p>
<a href="chsetopt.html">Internal parameters</a></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>

