<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>
<h2><font size=6>Hydrogen Set</font></h2><p>
This predefined set contains all the hydrogen and deuterium atoms
of the current molecule. This predefined set is equivalent to the
RasMol atom expression
"<tt><b>elemno=1</b></tt>"

<p>
<a href="predef.html">Predefined sets</a></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>

