<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>

<h2><font size=6>Chain Colours</font></h2><p>
The RasMol
<tt><b>chain</b></tt>
colour scheme assigns each macromolecular chain a unique colour. This
colour scheme is particularly useful for distinguishing the parts of
multimeric structure or the individual `strands' of a DNA chain.

<p>
<a href="chcolour.html">Colour schemes</a></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>

