<DOCNO>WT14-B39-246</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA057-000937-B016-50</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/intexpl/software/rasmol/hbondtyp.html 193.128.22.20 19970109091730 text/html 1324
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
