<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/netscape/science/actiontb/news2/art1.html 193.128.22.20 19970109092623 text/html 4544
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 09:16:32 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 24-Dec-96 11:30:57 GMT
Content-length: 4353
