<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/netscape/world/geneva/trans.html 193.128.22.20 19970109093229 text/html 6440
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 09:22:41 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 24-Dec-96 11:31:24 GMT
