<html><head><title>RasMol Manual: Aliphatic Set</title></head><body background="back1.gif" bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#1a1afa" vlink="30aa30"> <basefont size=4> <a 
<br clear=left>

<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><BR>
<h2><font size=6>Aliphatic Set</font></h2><p>
This set contains the aliphatic amino acids.
These are the amino acids Ala, Gly, Ile, Leu and Val.
This set is equiavlent to the RasMol atom expression
"<tt><b>ala, gly, ile, leu, val</b></tt>"

<p>
<a href="predef.html">Predefined sets</a></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>

