<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>
<h2><font size=6>Medium Set</font></h2><p>
All amino acids are classified as either
<a href="small.html"><tt><b>small,</b></tt></a>
<tt><b>medium</b></tt>
or
<a href="large.html"><tt><b>large.</b></tt></a>
This set is equivalent to the RasMol atom expression
"<tt><b>amino and not (large or small)</b></tt>"

