<html><head><title>RasMol Manual: Polar Set</title></head><body background="back1.gif" bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000" link="#1a1afa" vlink="30aa30"> <basefont 
<br clear=left>

<ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul><ul type=disc>

<h1><font size=7>RasMol manual</font></h1>
<hr size=4><br>

<h2><font size=6>Polar Set</font></h2><p>
This set contains the polar amino acids.
All amino acids are classified as either
<a href="hydroph.html"><tt><b>hydrophobic</b></tt></a>
or
<tt><b>polar.</b></tt>
This set is equivalent to the RasMol atom expression
"<tt><b>amino and not hydrophobic</b></tt>"

<p>
<a href="predef.html">Predefined sets</a></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul></ul>

</body>
</html>
