<DOCHDR>
http://ukweb1.glaxowellcome.co.uk:80/intexpl/science/nature/nature5b.html 193.128.22.20 19970109080730 text/html 4950
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
