<h3 align="center"><a name="info1"><b>ABOUT THE CHAMBER OF MINES
- FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</b></a></h3>
<div align="center"><center>

<table border="1" cellpadding="2" border>
    <tr>
        <th><a
        href="http://www.cs.wits.ac.za/faq/safrica/safrica.html"><font
