<DOCOLDNO>IA012-000121-B040-160</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://w3.bullion.org.za:80/releases/1997/comnum97.htm 196.26.82.193 19970217003830 text/html 8802
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 00:41:49 GMT
