src="http://www.bullion.org.za./tb104.gif" alt="Krugerrand"
border="0" width="101" height="17"></a> <a href="/new.htm"><img
src="http://www.bullion.org.za./tb105.gif" alt="What's New?"
border="0" width="101" height="17"></a> <a href="/info.htm"><img
src="http://www.bullion.org.za./tb106.gif" alt="Contacting us"
border="0" width="101" height="17"></a> </p>

<p align="left"><font size="2"><em> 1997, Chamber of Mines of
South Africa</em></font></p>
