<h3>Senior Management</h3>

<p>Senior management is based at the Chamber of Mines Building in
Hollard Street, Marshalltown, Johannesburg. An office also operates
in Cape Town from the Rhodes Building, 150 St Georges Mall, Cape
Town. Click <a href="work2.htm">HERE</a> for more information on the
core Management Structure. </p>

