        <p align="left">for more than 60 years, Mintek has been
        developing metallurgical and minerals-processing
        technology for one of the world's richest mining regions. Southern Africa
        has an exceptional wealth of mineral resources, including world-class
        deposits of gold, the platinum-group metals, diamonds,
        chromium and iron ores, the base metals, coal, and
        industrial minerals. Through innovative R&amp;D, Mintek
        aims to develop new and improved methods for extracting
        minerals and metals from ores, refining them, and
        processing them into value-added products. </p>
