<DOCNO>WT14-B39-468</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA013-000132-B016-216</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://w3.bullion.org.za:80/organisation/cvs/pollnow.htm 196.26.82.193 19970217013446 text/html 4082
