<h2 align=center><b><i>Core Services and Functions</i></b></h2>
<p align=center><img src="../images/line3.gif" align=bottom width=590 height=2></p>
<h3 align=center>PUBLIC POLICY UNIT</h3>
<p align=center>&#160; </p>
<hr size=3 noshade width=500>
<div align=center><center>
<table width=450>
<tr><td align=center width=50%><img src="../images/sa_flag2.gif" align=bottom width=160 height=86></td><td align=center width=70%><blockquote>
<p align=left><br>
<a href="#ABOUT"><font size=4><b>About the PPU</b></font></a></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
